### Tasks - Filter Tasks (Simple)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks/filter
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "listId": "list-uuid-here",
  "includeArchived": false,
  "filters": {
    "logic": "and",
    "conditions": [
      {
        "field": "status",
        "operator": "equals",
        "value": "status-uuid-here"
      },
      {
        "field": "assignee",
        "operator": "equals",
        "value": "user-uuid-here"
      }
    ]
  }
}

### Tasks - Filter Tasks (Complex with AND/OR)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks/filter
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "listId": "list-uuid-here",
  "includeArchived": false,
  "filters": {
    "logic": "and",
    "conditions": [
      {
        "field": "status",
        "operator": "in",
        "value": ["status-uuid-1", "status-uuid-2"]
      },
      {
        "field": "priority",
        "operator": "not_equals",
        "value": "priority-uuid-here"
      },
      {
        "field": "dueDate",
        "operator": "less_than_or_equal",
        "value": "2026-01-31"
      },
      {
        "conditions": [
          {
            "field": "tag",
            "operator": "equals",
            "value": "tag-uuid-1"
          },
          {
            "field": "tag",
            "operator": "equals",
            "value": "tag-uuid-2"
          }
        ],
        "logic": "or"
      }
    ]
  }
}

